result.content:
Hello all My first Blog Post here on Codeforces,

just wanted to tell you about my project AlgoWiki.

On Internet, There is a lot of knowledge on different topics scarred over different sources. Most of the knowledge is either online on the web or with the people as human knowledge. I want to create a repository as a platform to bind this scarred piece of knowledge at one place!

Topics We have Covered till now

  • Competitive Programming
  • Algorithms and their Implementation
  • Data Science Books and articles
  • Machine Learning
  • C
  • C++
  • HTML
  • JavaScript and
  • Interview Related Resources!!

Topic we have yet to cover

  • Artificial Intelligence
  • Discrete Mathematics
  • Graph Theory
  • Combinatorics
  • Game Theory etc!
    Please Contribute to this Repository
    Read Our Contribution Page Contributing to this repository
    You can Add links of different sources on different topics
    You can also create topics and add diffrent resources to it.
    Make sure that links that you provide should be related to the topic!

Project WebPage AlgoWiki

On GitHub

And We are collecting Websites and resources! Send files,pdfs,printed articles or your bookmark folder to me at tvicky002@gmail.com

Thank you! :)
